{"id":2411,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/2411","type":2,"name":"天使な小生意気","name_cn":"天使的小生意气","summary":"6年前，9岁的天使惠在一次机缘巧合下替一位巫士解了围，巫士送了他一本魔法书。就在打开书，天使惠对书中小丑许下成为男人中的男人这个愿望后，小丑竟然将他变成女人中的女人了.......目睹这一过程并知道真相的只有跟惠一起的好友花华院美木，而在其他人的记忆中惠是男孩子则被抹去。于是，惠就以这样一个让男生们流口水，让女生们妒忌的绝色美女身份过着这个被变身10年的校园生活……不过，“她”的性格仍然是好打架（连身手也是）的男性化。苏我源造，中学里面臭名远播的一名学生，不过自从跟惠见面之后就一直未打架赢过，更要让打败过他的惠来救，真的有够差劲了……。而在班上，藤木一郎、安田太助等人则成立了天使惠亲卫队，为了保护公主不惜一切？\r\n总而言之，天使小生意气就是一个充满搞笑的校园故事动漫。","eps":[{"id":14229,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/14229","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":14230,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/14230","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":14231,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/14231","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":14232,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/14232","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":14233,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/14233","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":14234,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/14234","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":14235,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/14235","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":14236,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/14236","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":14237,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/14237","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":14238,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/14238","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":14239,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/14239","type":0,"sort